data.description: PEACOCK CONSTRUCTION HAS DONE IT AGAIN......This gorgeous 3BR/2BA beauty has it all. Spacious family room leads into beautiful kitchen/dining area w/granite counter tops and loads of cabinets.  Split bedroom plan with vinyl plank flooring through out.  All baths have granite counter tops and master has a massive sized walk in closet.  There is a finished bonus room that has a variety of options,  covered back patio and 2/10 warranty are just a few of the many extras in this lovely home. HUGE PRICE REDUCTION TO $299,900!
